ify up to five custom or system actions inside a toast notification.","pos":[4120,4200]},{"content":"input<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;gt;</ph> This allows users to provide input, such as quick replying to a message, or selecting an option from a drop-down menu.","pos":[4209,4337],"source":"input&gt; This allows users to provide input, such as quick replying to a message, or selecting an option from a drop-down menu."},{"content":"Both <ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>action<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;gt;</ph> and <ph id=\"ph3\">&amp;lt;</ph>input<ph id=\"ph4\">&amp;gt;</ph> are adaptive within the Windows family of devices.","pos":[4339,4427],"source":"Both &lt;action&gt; and &lt;input&gt; are adaptive within the Windows family of devices."},{"content":"For example, on mobile or desktop devices, an <ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>action<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;gt;</ph> to a user is a button on which to tap/click.","pos":[4428,4533],"source":" For example, on mobile or desktop devices, an &lt;action&gt; to a user is a button on which to tap/click."},{"content":"A text <ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>input<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;gt;</ph> is a box in which users can input text using either a physical keyboard or an on-screen keyboard.","pos":[4534,4652],"source":" A text &lt;input&gt; is a box in which users can input text using either a physical keyboard or an on-screen keyboard."},{"content":"These elements will also adapt to future interaction scenarios, such as an action announced by voice or a text input taken by dictation.","pos":[4653,4789]},{"pos":[4791,5004],"content":"When an action is taken by the user, you can do one of the following by specifying the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>ActivationType<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/dn408447)</ept> attribute inside the <ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;lt;</ph>action<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;gt;</ph> element:","source":"When an action is taken by the user, you can do one of the following by specify